和警察对了几句，简单登记了一下就回来了。在路上突然又觉得，其实男生看起来也就20出头，长的也挺清秀的，可惜了。希望有了这个教训，男孩以后能够更加阳光~这里也提醒女生：万一遇到类似事情，及时求救，注意安全，坚决行动。", "timestamp": 1647834709}, {"allow_search": false, "attention": false, "author_title": null, "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "comments": [], "create_time": 1647834661, "cw": "政治相关", "hot_score": null, "is_blocked": false, "is_reported": null, "is_tmp": true, "last_comment_time": 1647834661, "likenum": 1, "n_attentions": 1, "n_comments": 0, "pid": 20385, "poll": null, "reply": 0, "text": "[tmp]\n![si03dsn65ho81 _1_.jpg](https://s2.loli.net/2022/03/21/R3PDjIs9lbFLAd2.jpg)", "timestamp": 1647834661}, {"allow_search": true, "attention": false, "author_title": null, "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "comments": [{"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 55564, "create_time": 1647835625, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "好好学基础课吧", "timestamp": 1647835625}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 55622, "create_time": 1647840128, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "问问老师？“我是大一学生但我想试试看，您觉得行吗，有什么必需的先修知识…”", "timestamp": 1647840128}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 55644, "create_time": 1647843152, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "一些打榜的比赛，或者科创活动更适合大一学生", "timestamp": 1647843152}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 55645, "create_time": 1647843176, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "主要以学技能，复现过去的理论，锻炼动手能力，用软件硬件为主", "timestamp": 1647843176}], "create_time": 1647834539, "cw": null, "hot_score": null, "is_blocked": false, "is_reported": null, "is_tmp": false, "last_comment_time": 1647843176, "likenum": 5, "n_attentions": 5, "n_comments": 4, "pid": 20382, "poll": null, "reply": 4, "text": "有什么适合大一菜鸟的srt项目吗？😂", "timestamp": 16